&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;우리는 게이머의 로망을 실현하기 위해, 누구도 가지 않는 길을 갑니다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;예상을 뛰어넘는 과감한 상상력과 기술로, 전 세계 팬들이 잊지 못할 세상을 만들기 위해 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;담대하게 도전하고 개척합니다.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;We pioneer the path to players&#39; dreams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;With bold imagination and breakthrough technology, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;we create unforgettable worlds for fans across the globe.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Engineer &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are KRAFTON – a collective of independent game development studios brought together to create innovative and engaging entertainment experiences for gamers across the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Since the release of our flagship title – PUBG: BATTLEGROUNDS – in 2017, it has become one of the highest-selling video games of all time with over 70 million copies sold.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are headquartered in Seoul, South Korea, with regional KRAFTON offices located across the globe. Our Amsterdam office is home to KRAFTON Europe, with several key product and publishing teams focused on Western markets based here, along with our Esports team. It is also home to the Black Budget development team, who are busy working on our upcoming new title.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The AI Ops Team sits within West Publishing Services (WPS) as KRAFTON Publishing&#39;s internal AI product team, embedded with Global Publishing teams, studios, and leadership - owning Community &amp;amp; Creator data across KRAFTON and turning it into decision-grade outputs and operational workflows for the stakeholders we serve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will join a four-person team (Lead, two PMs, one AI Engineer), deeply integrated in KRAFTON&#39;s Publishing work and in charge of building and shipping AI products with measurable impact on our publishing efforts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Basic Roles and Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Ideate, design, build and ship AI systems for community, creator, localization, and playtest publishing workflows as reliable, repeatable, accountable systems&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Own reliability, evaluation, observability, and security for AI products that interact with external stakeholders (e.g., creator email outreach, Community Manager response drafting, Steam key distribution under NDA)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Develop the MCP-first intelligence layer over AI Ops&#39; Creator and Community databases and reporting ecosystems&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Build and harden multi-agent systems with approval-gated workflows (CRM creator outreach, CM response assistance, PR agent workflows, title risk analysis)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Drive the Community Alert System (real-time sentiment-drop and issue-spike detection with Slack escalation and CM-facing response support)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Contribute to an in-game dialogue framework R&amp;amp;D (Unity/Unreal-importable, safety-controlled)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required experience: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Software engineering experience, including building production AI/ML or LLM-based systems in a professional environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Strong understanding of reliability, evaluation, observability, and security practices for AI systems that interact with external services or end users&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Proficiency in Python and modern AI/ML tooling&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Experience building and maintaining data pipelines at meaningful scale (millions of records per month)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Strong analytical and structured problem-solving skills, with the ability to ship working systems independently and operate them in production&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Ability to explain and communicate technical problems and solutions clearly to non-technical colleagues and teams&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Business-level proficiency in English&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;“Nice to have” experience: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Bachelor’s degree (or higher) in a related field&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Experience or knowledge (or interest!) in the video games industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Experience with the AI APIs (prompt-engineering, tool use, and evaluation at scale)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Experience designing and operating MCP servers and integrating LLM tools with structured data sources&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Some proficiency in the Korean language would be great, but not in any way required! &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- A competitive salary&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- An allowance to cover the Dutch mandatory health insurance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- 25 paid + 4 extra paid working days off a year&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Relocation package&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Pension scheme&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- A commuter allowance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Lunch allowance and a range of snacks &amp;amp; drinks&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Health and Wellness allowance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Full assistance with visas and the 30% ruling applications when the candidate is eligible&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;More about our Amsterdam office…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our office is situated in the Amsterdam Zuid area, a buzzing business hub in the southern part of the city. &lt;br&gt;Close to our office you can find a broad choice of cuisine – such as the iconic Market 33 Food Hall, offering vibrant social settings.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Also, nearby is one of the main public transportation hubs – Amsterdam Zuid train, metro, tram &amp;amp; bus station, bringing the city’s highlights close, be it one of the many museums, canals, parks, or culinary experiences you are interested in.&lt;br&gt;Likewise, our Amsterdam team reflects the city’s diverse atmosphere – being mainly expats, we currently represent more than 40 different nationalities, and we are still expanding our team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We welcome all applications!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are proud to have such a multicultural environment and we strive to create a safe, inclusive, and harmonious atmosphere for everyone to thrive in. We invite applications from all genders, sexual orientations, races, colors, religions, and ages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If this sounds like a good fit for your skills and experience, then apply right away!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
